{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/use-the-bootstrap-grid-to-put-elements-side-by-side","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Koristite Bootstrap mrežu za postavljanje elemenata jedan pored drugog","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Bootstrap koristi 12-kolonski sistem mreže koji se prilagođava uređaju, što olakšava postavljanje elemenata u redove i određivanje širine svakog elementa na konzistentan način. Mnoge Bootstrap klase mogu se primeniti na <code>div</code> element.</p>\n<p>Bootstrap ima različite predizme kolona koje koristi zavisno od širine ekrana korisnika. Na primer, telefoni imaju uže ekrane, dok laptopovi imaju širi ekrane.</p>\n<p>Uzmete za primer Bootstrap klasu <code>col-md-*</code>. Ovde, <code>md</code> znači srednji (medium), a <code>*</code> je broj koji određuje koliko kolona bi element trebao imati po širini. U ovom slučaju, određuje se širina kolone elementa na ekranu srednje veličine, kao što je laptop.</p>\n<p>U aplikaciji za fotografije mačaka koju gradimo, koristićemo <code>col-xs-*</code>, gde <code>xs</code> znači veoma mali (kao ekran vrlo malog telefona), a <code>*</code> je broj koji određuje koliko kolona bi element trebao imati po širini.</p>\n<p>Postavite dugmad 'Like', 'Info' i 'Delete' jedan pored drugog tako što ćete sve tri rasporediti unutar jednog elementa <code>&#x3C;div class=\"row\"></code>, a zatim svako u elementu <code>&#x3C;div class=\"col-xs-4\"></code>.</p>\n<p>Klasa <code>row</code> dodaje se na <code>div</code>, a sama dugmad mogu se rasporediti unutar njega.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad88fee1348ce8acef08815","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18371,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/use-the-bootstrap-grid-to-put-elements-side-by-side"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\r\n<style>\r\n  .red-text {\r\n    color: red;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  h2 {\r\n    font-family: Lobster, Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  p {\r\n    font-size: 16px;\r\n    font-family: Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .thick-green-border {\r\n    border-color: green;\r\n    border-width: 10px;\r\n    border-style: solid;\r\n    border-radius: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .smaller-image {\r\n    width: 100px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h2 class=\"red-text text-center\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\r\n\r\n  <p>Click here for <a href=\"#\">cat photos</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n  <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"smaller-image thick-green-border\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\r\n\r\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Tuxedo cats running on dirt ground.\">\r\n  <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-primary\">Like</button>\r\n  <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-info\">Info</button>\r\n  <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-danger\">Delete</button>\r\n  <p>Things cats love:</p>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>catnip</li>\r\n    <li>laser pointers</li>\r\n    <li>lasagna</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\r\n  <ol>\r\n    <li>flea treatment</li>\r\n    <li>thunder</li>\r\n    <li>other cats</li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Indoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Loving</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Crazy</label>\r\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\r\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\r\n  </form>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Sva vaša dugmad treba da budu raspoređena unutar jednog <code>div</code> elementa sa klasom <code>row</code>.</p>","testString":"const row = document.querySelector('div.row');\r\nconst rowChildren = row?.querySelectorAll(`:scope ${'button'}`); \r\nassert.lengthOf(rowChildren, 3);"},{"text":"<p>Svako vaše Bootstrap dugme treba da bude raspoređeno unutar svog <code>div</code> elementa sa klasom <code>col-xs-4</code>.</p>","testString":"const columns = document.querySelectorAll('div.col-xs-4');\r\n\r\nconst firstButton = columns?.[0]?.querySelectorAll(`:scope ${'button'}`)\r\nassert.lengthOf(firstButton,1);\r\n\r\nconst secondButton = columns?.[1]?.querySelectorAll(`:scope ${'button'}`)\r\nassert.lengthOf(secondButton,1);\r\n\r\nconst thirdButton = columns?.[2]?.querySelectorAll(`:scope ${'button'}`)\r\nassert.lengthOf(thirdButton,1);\r\n"},{"text":"<p>Svaki vaš <code>button</code> element treba da ima zatvarajući tag.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/<\\/button>/g);\r\nassert.match(code,/<button/g);\r\nassert.equal(code.match(/<\\/button>/g).length , code.match(/<button/g).length);"},{"text":"<p>Svaki vaš <code>div</code> element treba da ima zatvarajući tag.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/<\\/div>/g);\r\nassert.match(code,/<div/g);\r\nassert.equal(code.match(/<\\/div>/g).length , code.match(/<div/g).length);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#bootstrap","dashedName":"use-the-bootstra